targets.query:
SELECT sum("OK") / sum("ALL")
FROM (
    SELECT sum("count") as "OK"
    FROM "jmeter"
    WHERE ("transaction"::tag =~ /^ur.*/ AND "statut"::tag = 'ok' AND "generator"::tag =~ /^$generator$/ AND "profile_name"::tag =~ /^$profile_name$/ AND "system_name"::tag =~ /^$system_name$/) AND $timeFilter
    GROUP BY time(30s) fill(null)
),
(
    SELECT sum("count") as "ALL"
    FROM "jmeter"
    WHERE ("transaction"::tag =~ /^ur.*/ AND "statut"::tag = 'all' AND "generator"::tag =~ /^$generator$/ AND "profile_name"::tag =~ /^$profile_name$/ AND "system_name"::tag =~ /^$system_name$/) AND $timeFilter
    GROUP BY time(30s) fill(null)
)

SELECT sum("KO") / sum("ALL")
FROM (
    SELECT sum("count") as "KO"
    FROM "jmeter"
    WHERE ("transaction"::tag =~ /^ur.*/ AND "statut"::tag = 'ko' AND "generator"::tag =~ /^$generator$/ AND "profile_name"::tag =~ /^$profile_name$/ AND "system_name"::tag =~ /^$system_name$/) AND $timeFilter
    GROUP BY time(30s) fill(null)
),
(
    SELECT sum("count") as "ALL"
    FROM "jmeter"
    WHERE ("transaction"::tag =~ /^ur.*/ AND "statut"::tag = 'all' AND "generator"::tag =~ /^$generator$/ AND "profile_name"::tag =~ /^$profile_name$/ AND "system_name"::tag =~ /^$system_name$/) AND $timeFilter
    GROUP BY time(30s) fill(null)
)

SELECT sum("count") FROM /^$measurement$/ WHERE ("transaction"::tag =~ /^ur.*/ AND "generator"::tag =~ /^$generator$/ AND "profile_name"::tag =~ /^$profile_name$/ AND "system_name"::tag =~ /^$system_name$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction"::tag, "statut"::tag
SELECT sum("count") FROM /^$measurement$/ WHERE ("statut"::tag = 'ko' OR "statut"::tag = 'all') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "transaction", "statut"
